the art of the apology
mood swings caused by varying blood sugar levels can often lead to hurt feelings and relational wounds. One of the most important steps in healing relationbships is a heartfelt apology.

Consider: how would yoyu like someone to apologize to you?

Consider: how would the other person attempt to apologize back?

